                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-244" type="surname" value="BAILEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-244" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN BAILEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Tothill-street, Grays'-inn-lane, and am a coach-smith—the prisoner worked in our shop for one week before the 1st of July—he slept in the same room with me. On the morning of the 1st of July he got up at four o'clock, and at seven I missed my coat and the other things stated—this is ray coat—(<hi rend="italic">looking at it</hi>.)</p>
